rComments: I have him as a visiting prof at Cardozo. The textbook can be dry but Prof. B injects class with humor & wit. He is so funny & entertaining (lots of pop culture jokes). Wish he wasn't going back to Chi, I would definitely take more classes. (Haven't taken the final yet, so I don't know how difficult his exams are) but lectures are awesome.
One of the worst teachers ever.
